#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.special.erfinv.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.special.erfinv"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.err_fresnel.erfinv:1 of
msgid "Inverse of the error function."
msgstr "误差函数的反函数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.err_fresnel.erfinv:3 of
msgid "Computes the inverse of the error function."
msgstr "计算误差函数的反函数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.err_fresnel.erfinv:5 of
msgid ""
"In the complex domain, there is no unique complex number w satisfying "
"erf(w)=z. This indicates a true inverse function would be multivalued. "
"When the domain restricts to the real, -1 < x < 1, there is a unique real"
" number satisfying erf(erfinv(x)) = x."
msgstr ""
"在复数域中，不存在唯一的复数 w 满足 erf(w)=z。这表明真正的反函数将是多值"
"的。当定义域限制在实数范围 -1 < x < 1 时，存在唯一的实数满足 erf(erfinv(x"
")) = x。"

#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.special.erfinv.rst
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.err_fresnel.erfinv:10 of
msgid "Argument at which to evaluate. Domain: [-1, 1]"
msgstr "用于计算的参数。定义域：[-1, 1]"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.err_fresnel.erfinv:12 of
msgid "Optional output array for the function values"
msgstr "可选的输出数组，用于存储函数值"

#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.special.erfinv.rst
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.err_fresnel.erfinv:15 of
msgid "**erfinv** -- The inverse of erf of y, element-wise"
msgstr "**erfinv** -- y 的误差函数的反函数，逐元素计算"

#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.special.erfinv.rst
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.err_fresnel.erfinv:20 of
msgid ":py:obj:`erf`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.err_fresnel.erfinv:21 of
msgid "Error function of a complex argument"
msgstr "复数参数的误差函数"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.err_fresnel.erfinv:23 of
msgid ":py:obj:`erfc`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.err_fresnel.erfinv:24 of
msgid "Complementary error function, ``1 - erf(x)``"
msgstr "互补误差函数，``1 - erf(x)``"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.err_fresnel.erfinv:26 of
msgid ":py:obj:`erfcinv`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.err_fresnel.erfinv:27 of
msgid "Inverse of the complementary error function"
msgstr "互补误差函数的反函数"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.err_fresnel.erfinv:30 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.err_fresnel.erfinv:31 of
msgid ""
"This function wraps the ``erf_inv`` routine from the Boost Math C++ "
"library [1]_."
msgstr "此函数封装了来自 Boost Math C++ 库的 ``erf_inv`` 例程 [1]_。"

